findings.title: Exposed Anthropic API Key in Source Code
findings.description: Hardcoded Anthropic API Key found in source code at line 217
findings.impact: Attackers can extract Anthropic API Key and gain unauthorized access to systems/APIs
findings.recommendation: Remove hardcoded Anthropic API Key, use environment variables (.env), add to .gitignore, revoke and regenerate key

findings.title: Command Injection Vulnerability
findings.description: Shell command injection detected at line 29
findings.impact: Attackers can execute arbitrary command commands
findings.recommendation: Use subprocess with shell=False and validate inputs

findings.title: Missing Authentication on API Endpoints
findings.description: API endpoints exposed without authentication middleware
findings.impact: Unauthorized users can access sensitive API functionality and data
findings.recommendation: Implement JWT/OAuth authentication, add Depends(verify_token) to all routes
